deposit(uint256[],address[],uint256,addr.details: Deposits tokens in the given pool. Creates new Farm contract if there isn't one deployed for the lpPair and deposits tokens.

params.amountLP: - Amounts of LP tokens to deposit.
params.lpPair: - Address of the pool to deposit tokens in.
params.recipient: - Address which will recieve the deposit.

returns.liquidity: - Total liquidity sent to the farm (in lpTokens).

distribute(address,(uint256,uint256,addr.details: Distributes tokens between users for a single {Farms[lpPair]}.

params.assets: - The data used to swap reward tokens for the needed tokens.
params.funds: - The data used to swap reward tokens for the needed tokens.
params.limits: - The data used to swap reward tokens for the needed tokens. Note: This function can only be called by the distributor.
params.rewardTokens: - Reward tokens to recieve from the pool.
params.swaps: - The data used to swap reward tokens for the needed tokens.

totalDeposits(address).details: Returns total amount locked in the pool. Doesn't take pending rewards into account.

params.lpPair: - LP pool to check total deposits in.

params._address: - The address to check stakes for.
params.lpPair: - LP pool to check stakes in.

withdraw(address,uint256,bool,address).details: Withdraws tokens from the given pool.

params.recipient: - The address which will recieve tokens.
params.withdrawLP: - True: Withdraw in LP tokens, False: Withdraw in normal tokens.
